metadata.name: This Year's Love
metadata.description:
This year's love will be a history to many. It will also be the catalyst of hope, peace, and joy to continue each purpose in the years to come. In every ending, there is a new beginning to change, develop, and learn to become better. **This year's love will be a history to many. It will also be the catalyst of hope, peace, and joy to continue each purpose in the years to come. In every ending, there is a new beginning to change, develop, and learn to become better. The question that we need to ask  ourselves is, "How much love can you give?"**
